# Thriving Places Index

## Description

The Thriving Places Index measures the local conditions for wellbeing, and whether those conditions are being delivered fairly and sustainably. It consists of a broad set of indicators grouped into these three headline domains, from datasets produced by established national data agencies such as theâ€¦

